# 1.7 Site collection administrator

## summary

Verify site collection administrators can see everything in a site collection regardless of role assignments.

## steps

* create a user `usr1_7`
* set `usr1_7` as a site collection administrator.
* create a site collection `sc1_7`
* add a site, list, list items with default permissions.
* crawl `sc1_7`

## assertions

* verify security trimming allows `usr1_7` to see all the search results. 
